      <p class="- topic/p ">Power Invoice Generation ​​​​​​​for Salesforce Billing has the following limitations:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Customers can only generate documents from the objects within the Salesforce Billing installed package (those with the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">blng</i> prefix).</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Word and HTML Email are the only supported template types.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Email and PDF are the only output file types.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Up to 1,000 invoices per month.</li>
      </ul>
